# SSL Certificates Directory

Place your SSL certificates here for HTTPS support.

## Structure

```
ssl/
├── spotexsrl.com.crt
├── spotexsrl.com.key
├── agency.spotexsrl.com.crt
├── agency.spotexsrl.com.key
├── admin.spotexsrl.com.crt
└── admin.spotexsrl.com.key
```

## Generate Self-Signed Certificates (Development Only)

```bash
openssl req -x509 -nodes -days 365 -newkey rsa:2048 \
  -keyout spotexsrl.com.key \
  -out spotexsrl.com.crt \
  -subj "/CN=spotexsrl.com"
```

## Production

Use Let's Encrypt or your SSL provider's certificates.
